headline: New Data Center Announced; SWEPCO Role Cited in Supporting Local Economic Growth
summary: Southwestern Electric Power Co. (SWEPCO) announced a new data center investment from Amazon that company leaders describe as the most significant economic development win Northwest Louisiana has seen in a generation. This investment brings new utility infrastructure upgrades that will deliver meaningful, long‑term benefits for SWEPCO customers while also supporting Amazon's data center operations.
